## Emergency Procedures

### Quick Fixes
```bash
# Amend last commit if not pushed (e.g., fix typo)
git add main.tex
git commit --amend --no-edit

# Reset soft for reworking recent commits
git reset --soft HEAD~1
```

### Recovery
```bash
# View commit history
git log --oneline -10

# Recover lost commits
git reflog
```

